The evidence with the title 'The political one percent of the one percent : Sunlight Foundation ' says Dec 13, 2011  ... In the 2010 election cycle , 26,783 individuals (or slightly less than one in ten thousand Americans ) each contributed more than $10,000 to federal political campaigns . Combined, these donors spent $774 million. That's 24.3% of the total from individuals to politicians , parties, PACs, and independent  ... 
